matt birkbeck is an american author and investigative journalist, whose articles have appeared in the new york times, playboy, the philadelphia inquirer, reader's digest, boston magazine and people." a former newspaper reporter, birkbeck worked at the morning call., where he was cited for his lengthy investigative pieces on pennsylvania's flawed gaming initiative. in 2010 he joined business publisher harrison scott publications, where he covers wall street and regulatory issues in washington, d.c.